Added SetterMethod for Ship on board. Changed naming scheme for no good reason other then aesthetics: DON'T EVER DO THAT AGAIN!!!

jdoc and small bug-fixes

rewrote Shipsavailable for easier debugging. Didn't find the bug tho..
Resolved all Bugs. Problem laid in the way how a fieldstatus was received. It wasn't coupled to the status of the ship.
